rows.label: qst103319_msg001
rows.name: グーラの為にやったことだ(仮)

rows.label: qst103319_msg002
rows.name: やめとけ(仮)

rows.label: qst103319_msg003
rows.name: 捕まえてくれ(仮)

rows.label: qst103319_msg004
rows.name: どうする？

rows.label: qst103319_msg005
rows.name: 助ける(仮)

rows.label: qst103319_msg006
rows.name: 助けない(仮)

rows.label: qst103319_msg0001
rows.name: I wonder if she had a family...

rows.label: qst103319_msg0002
rows.name: They must be worried sick.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0101
rows.name: I'm deeply sorry to ask this of you.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0201
rows.name:
That's the transportation of the
body to Military HQ all sorted!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0202
rows.name: Thanks.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0203
rows.name: An organization of anti-imperialists...?

rows.label: qst103319_msg0204
rows.name:
I've only really just arrived in
the capital so I've not heard
of anything like that.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0205
rows.name:
Oh, but I do have one new
clue to offer!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0206
rows.name:
We found fresh footprints on the
top of the cliff just above here.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0207
rows.name:
One of the other officers headed
up there to investigate, but I haven't
heard anything from him yet.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0208
rows.name:
Could you go see what he's
up to, please?

rows.label: qst103319_msg0209
rows.name:
Oh, yes - to get there, you'll need to
open a locked gate! It's meant to be
off-limits to non-military personnel, see.

rows.label: qst103319_msg0210
rows.name:
Here, I'll give you the key.
Take good care of it!

rows.label: qst103319_msg0301
rows.name:
You'll find the investigating officer
up on top of the cliff. Let me know
if he's found anything useful!
